data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***UPDATED with gorgeous wood-look Luxury Vinyl Plank in the downstairs, except in Wet Areas. **** Welcome to this delightful townhome located in a gated community in the Westchase area with A-Rated schools. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a powder room, this home offers comfortable living spaces within 1,857 sq.ft. Relax and enjoy the outdoors on the screened patio, which provides a private retreat with wooded views. Great Room combines the SPACIOUS Family Room, Dining Area + Kitchen. Step into the spacious kitchen and be captivated by the WHITE 42" WOOD cabinetry, providing ample storage for all your culinary needs. The farmhouse sink and granite countertops add a touch of elegance, while the stainless steel appliances complete the modern look. Refrigerator [2021]; Dishwasher [2023]; Range [2019] + updated farmhouse sink & faucet. Current owner lovingly maintained & updated the home including adding the SCREENED Lanai. Fresh Paint [2023]; EV Charger added in Garage, Powder Room vanity and 3 new toilets + updated faucets. You’ll enjoy the LARGE Master Bedroom, 2 pantry closets and En-Suite Bath. Master Bathroom boasts dual vanity, shower stall & linen closet. Washer/Dryer convey with the home. Water & Sewer included in the monthly dues. The community amenities include a public pool where you can cool off and unwind, as well as two playgrounds where children can have fun and play. Additionally, you'll appreciate the convenience of nearby shopping and dining options that cater to your needs.  With its inviting layout, serene surroundings, and family-friendly amenities, this townhome with its well-appointed kitchen is the perfect place to call home.
